{"tid":239180,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)白宮仆街 霧地異煞 追債大亂鬥","createTime":"2017-05-11T13:23:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-11T18:26:46.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6facb663284aa4d65c432b1db942bf86b10b8508","tid":239180,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T13:23:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2F&d=y7rvae0RAf6wlyT0SQBX%2BNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=2a4e8518\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/</a> CC台又執柒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=y7rvae0RAf6wlyT0SQBX%2BNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=5d6b2972\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a>可以直接睇到V台<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=y7rvae0RAf6wlyT0SQBX%2BNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=305032ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/b/bf/Olympus_Has_Fallen_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fb%2Fbf%2FOlympus_Has_Fallen_poster.jpg&h=511003d1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/a/a1/The_Mist_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fa%2Fa1%2FThe_Mist_poster.jpg&h=28c6da5c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTc2NjgyMzAxNV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTIxNTE4MjE@._V1_UY1200_CR115,0,630,1200_AL_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-na.ssl-images-amazon.com%2Fimages%2FM%2FMV5BMTc2NjgyMzAxNV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTIxNTE4MjE%40._V1_UY1200_CR115%2C0%2C630%2C1200_AL_.jpg&h=5d18b57a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.麥克&middot;班寧是一名美國陸軍遊騎兵退役的美國特勤局隊員，多年來盡職地保護總統班傑明&middot;埃什與他的家人。在一次聖誕節前夕，班傑明與自己的妻子瑪姬和兒康納到『大衛營』度假回去時，在一座橋上因雪天路滑而導致車禍，總統轎車也剛好被卡在橋上而下墜，但麥克因情況急迫而只將班傑明直接拉出汽車，而第一夫人則是跟隨汽車掉下橋梁墜亡。事情過後，班傑明與康納處於長時間的悲痛期，麥克也因為此事而造成難以抹去的心理陰影，於是退出特勤隊調至美國財政部的保全工作...<br />\n<br />\n2.一場暴風雨，鄰居諾頓律師的樹木倒塌，打壞電影海報畫家大衛德雷頓（湯瑪斯&middot;傑恩飾）的畫室，大衛和他的妻子看見不尋常的霧開始從山間蔓延，全鎮亦斷電。為重整風暴摧殘後的家園，大衛和5歲的兒子比利（納桑&middot;蓋博飾），與鄰居諾頓（安德魯&middot;布瑞格飾）去當地的超市採賣物品。到了店內，越來越多的警車在街上奔馳，引起顧客注意，最終空襲警報響起，一名老人丹米勒（傑佛瑞&middot;狄蒙飾）滿面鮮血，狼狽的跑進超市，警告大家有迎面而來的濃霧中有異物，非常駭人<br />\n<br />\n3.史崔奇是個潦倒的禮車司機，被黑幫下了最後通牒，午夜前要償還賭債。他選擇載送趕時間的富豪，瘋狂在洛杉磯的大街小巷中狂飆，和時間賽跑。究竟他能否順利籌到錢，為自己買一個明天呢？<br />\n<br />\n9 30PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10d9fdfd492fdd27177c0518e1b238760f2668ba","tid":239180,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T13:51:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"695ec6146f22a09042d6d9c66ef4ed3fc8c8bb22","tid":239180,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T14:16:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"349ef00a90fa04c0f2336aff43643afb5f1227c7","tid":239180,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T14:40:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9a